        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## worker-sidecar — pull loop & IPC pool\n`ipc_pool_inflight` flatlining at `SIE_IPC_POOL_SIZE` is the canonical symptom of a too-small IPC pool. Rule of thumb: keep `SIE_PULL_LOOP_INFLIGHT ≤ SIE_MAX_CONCURRENT_BATCHES ≤ SIE_IPC_POOL_SIZE`."
      }
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
