        "content": "## Rust scheduler — adaptive controller\nIf `sie_worker_scheduler_batch_items` stays tiny while `sie_worker_scheduler_adaptive_fill_ratio` is low, the sidecar is flushing before work accumulates. Check `SIE_BATCHER_COALESCE_MS`, `SIE_BATCHER_MAX_BATCH_REQUESTS`, and the `SIE_ADAPTIVE_*` quantum knobs before changing Python adapter settings."
      }
