      "description": "FP16 pipe ratio over the full device: our gte-multilingual-base runs in torch.float16 and its flash-attn GEMMs dispatch onto the FP16 pipe. HMMA (Tensor Core) is a subset; if TENSOR_ACTIVE < FP16_ACTIVE the attention impl is not hitting tensor cores (varlen flash-attn does).",
